headline: Zimmer Biomet Receives FDA Clearance for OsseoFit™ Stemless Shoulder System for Total Shoulder Replacement
summary: Zimmer Biomet Holdings, Inc. (NYSE and SIX: ZBH), a global medical technology leader, today announced U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) 510(k) clearance for the OsseoFit™ Stemless Shoulder System for total shoulder replacement. This innovative implant is designed to match the natural humeral (upper shoulder bone) anatomy1-3 to optimize anatomical fit while maximizing preservation of healthy bone. The OsseoFit Stemless Shoulder System expands the company's expansive total shoulder portfolio
